description: Beautifully updated 1-bedroom condo in the heart of South Boston! This sun-filled unit features hardwood floors, recessed lighting, and an open layout with a modern kitchen — granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and white shaker cabinets. The bathroom offers a marble vanity, tile surround, and sleek matte black fixtures.Located just minutes from Broadway Station, the Seaport, shops, and restaurants. The building was fully gut renovated in 2009. Perfect for first-time buyers, investors, or anyone looking for easy city living in a prime location.
